Package: ctdnaTM
Type: Package
Title: ctDNA Deliverables
Version: 0.75.3
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Hamid", family = "Nikbakht",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "hamid.nikbakht@noreply.github.com")
  )
Description: Standardised plotting, statistics, and multi-modal integration
    helpers for the eight core ctDNA deliverables built around the
    Guardant Health Infinity platform but extensible to other vendors.
    Provides a grammar of variant filter schemes (rule / allOf / anyOf /
    not) with three built-in biomarker schemes (TSG_Tier1, TSG_Tier2,
    HRR14) plus a permissive impactful-alterations scheme (scheme_basic).
    Every exported function is documented for RStudio tooltip and tab
    autocomplete via roxygen2.
